originalText.text: Fast processing and clear, consistent feedback. They care about their customers beyond just the visa services. UPS lost my passport and Mr. Mohammad from Fast Visa Services worked with me until we tracked it and found it. He even gave me his own personal cell phone number to contact him at any time. He showed great care and compassion throughout the process. Overall a fantastic experience. They are trustworthy and worth your money. I definitely recommend anyone to work with them if they want to get any visa.
